tldr: The user requested a "Surprise me" button to open a random post. This
  button should use the existing button component with the secondary variant and
  be placed at the top right of the page.
overview: The user wants to add a new "Surprise me" feature to the application.
  This feature will be triggered by a button that, when clicked, will display a
  random post. The button needs to be styled using the existing button component
  with its secondary variant and positioned in the top right corner of the
  interface for prominent visibility.
